{"tid":1812163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到攬炒巴睇到】我地要眾籌唱衰香港","createTime":"2020-01-05T09:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T09:53:17.000Z","uid":124636,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3049dc2dd57d879682c87539d1cba22c72987021","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"繼1/1銅鑼灣後，今晚上水又玩大濫捕，相信鄧小強同佢班狗嚟緊都會用依一招<br />\n<br />\n鄧小強玩大濫捕，我地就將香港旅遊城市依個朵徹底摧毀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806934</a><br />\n<br />\n承接上文，對一大班好嬲但唔夠膽勇武嘅和理非手足，眾籌登報唱衰香港，叫所有人唔好再嚟香港或者係一個方法<br />\n<br />\n推到比攬炒巴睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a37e106841f6e9ee58ba6d9179fc6673dbd358d","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"9bdc8ca39fa0c66c90720e064e6fe9f9f3f0a9ed","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"5a0939db135fcea1feffaa78027d4088e5d0f7ab","tid":1812163,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43f250c5f8cfc87a1b5e112b9e76cfb13d683ebb","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"6fec42b66410657bc0edf73919783d0cef6857b7","tid":1812163,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">振興黃色經濟 拒絕幫襯建制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府正用盡一切手段迫企業歸邊，為示威者樹敵，為求社會各界與抗爭人士割蓆<br />\n<br />\n同時黑警透過非法濫捕，圖阻嚇港人和平表達訴求，損害港人自由，有違基本法28條原意<br />\n<br />\n警謊「自己人」裝修銀行為由，中斷民陣元旦百萬人遊行<br />\n<br />\n比你捉到便衣狗係為咗養成捉鬼文化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avbtvJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavbtvJ0.jpg&h=e1c98503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"666f9bfce130bcb37b2cc5d00405b271e26dc4e1","tid":1812163,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"想幫手足報仇，就要揾中資算帳<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb5066ae0d432ea011043f7ae094e407dfa4653e","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T09:59:28.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"2007a2bc92bd57172bde99085a0bfea816b4e40b","tid":1812163,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e9928cc572b46bab11ed20970f2fccad47b6b77","tid":1812163,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"6241363be012db5440bdd1358fd8bb26555fb5b7","tid":1812163,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"